author: The Current
description:
Watch "The End" by Of Monsters and Men recorded live at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

On a recent visit to The Current studio, Ragnar and Nanna from Of Monsters and Men performed this beautiful live rendition of "The End," a song from the band's latest album, "All Is Love and Pain in the Mouse Parade."

Of Monsters and Men’s 2025 album, All Is Love and Pain in the Mouse Parade, is available on Skarkali Records/Virgin Music Group.

Musicians
Nanna Bryndis Hilmarsdottir - vocals, guitar
Ragnar Thorhallsson - vocals, guitar, piano
